\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11674240 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 Well integrity. Yes. Honesty and integrity were - were deemed a great - value. Under all circumstances. And good social principles. T
hey liked people with principle as they called it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7634190 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 What did they think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11674240 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 They strongly disapproved of swearing which training I still feel. The ab}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10380228\charrsid19052 
sence of a swearing vocabulary e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 nforced a rather inarticulate boy as I was to expand his vocabulary in a proper direction.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7634190 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11674240 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 Taught not to chip in when adults were speaking. But remember listening - listening avidly with puzzlement sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7634190 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 If you did something your parents disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11674240 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 We were told off. We were chastised. But I never remember being struck by either parent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7634190 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 Do you remember any particular occasion when you were punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11674240 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 No, I don't remember any particular occasion but
 rarely - very rarely we were sometimes went to bed early which was deemed a punishment. We had a strong sense of shame or guilt if chastised and this seemed more effective in correction than physical punishment.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7634190 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 Would you say you received the ideas you had about how to behave from both your parents or did one play a more important part than the other?

