\insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 ed by a special tea and a present. Mother never knew her birthday owing to - the breakup of her home when she was a chil
d thorough the death of her parents so we gave her the first of January, New Year's day because of Scottish link. I don't remember birthday pres - birthday guests.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7634190 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 Can you remember anything you did with your mother and father together on Christmas Day?
