Well - father filled the Christmas stocking which was - first a brand new penny and then an apple and an orange and then the other things on top. And they were long stockings. We thought it was Father Christmas 'til I remember suspecting parents as
 being the benefactors so my sister and I resolved to stay awake, playing possum, to find out. But we fell asleep. And I don't remember how disillusionment came.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7634190 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 Did you have any musical instruments in the home?
