istmas.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7634190 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 And all he gets for it is the interest from the bank?
