 and that was my grandfather's pound a month bit. But I would rather like if I could to hear it to check I gave - and put any amendments at the end. That's all right then. Well I've heard the - for the sake of accuracy I've heard the playback of these tap
e
s and in the main they are accurate. However some slips of the tongue have occurred. First - early on the first half of the first tape I said my sister instead of their sister, my mother when referring to the break up of my mother's home when she was a ch
ild. Second, later on the same tape I said, when as a child playing marbles in the ring on a waste}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14381726\charrsid19052 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 
ground I described a marble that was stolen from me as a magical blood ollie - as a magical chinese marble but it should have been a ; for that particular inc
ident it should have been a magical blood ollie and the description that I've given refers to that particular type of ollie. third point. Nearly three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14381726\charrsid19052  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
