t to London from Egremont but were - where I said we returned soon after from London to Egremont this should have been from London to Liverpool. Fourth - at the end of the second half of the first tape I went to some from of educational cause while at wor
k until nearly forty years of age. I think I've mentioned two ages on the tape but forty is more accurate.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7634190 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 Would you be good enough to tell me again about Bloody Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11674240 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14951568\charrsid19052 Oh yes. Well the fifth item among the errors and omissions, I omitted to mention that my father supported}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
